quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,20,"∆Āeen …ďe ngonaani laawotoo…ďe ka leydi, laatanaaki …ďe kadi weldii…ďe gaanin Alla, he…ďe cowayanee lepte …óeen. ∆Āe laatanooki hattan…ďe nangol, …ďe ngonaano kadi yi'oo…ďe."
  11,21,"Ko …ďe ngoni sooyin…ďe woŇčkiiji mun …óin. …óuum ko …ďe pekintonoo majji gaay e ma…ď…ďe."
  11,22,"Sikke alah, won`de …ďen …óon ka laakara, ko kam…ďe …ďuroyta sooyude."
  11,23,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe, …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, …ďe njankinanii Joomi ma…ď…ďe, ko …ďe ngoni yim…ďe Aljanna …ďen, kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe toon."
  11,24,"Misal pe…óle …ói…ói …óe: ko wano bum…óo e pah…óu…óo, e ji'oowo e nanoowo. E …ďee …óoo …ói…ói fotat e misal? E on mbaajitotaako?"
  11,25,"Wollahi min nuliri Nuuhu e yim…ďe makko …ďen: "miin wonan¬īde on ko mi jertinoowo …ďanngin…óo.(pee√Ī…óo.)"
  11,26,"won¬īde wota on ndew si wanah Alla. min mi…óo hulani on lepte √Īalaande mu¬īusnde"."
  11,27,"Mbatu …ďeen yeddu…ďe e yim…ďe makko …ďen mbi'i: min nji'aani ma si wonah ko a …ďanndiŇčke sifa amen, men nj'aani kadi …ďen jokku…ďe ma si wo- naa jaas…ďe amen faa…óu…ďe feere, men nji'anaani on e amen …ďural. Worin mi…óen cikki ko on fenoo…ďe"."
  11,28,"O maaki: "eehey mon yo yim…ďe am, kaalnee kam si tawii mi…óo e …ďanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi am, O wee…óii kam yurmeende (Annabaaku) immorde ka makko, …óuum wumna e moo…óon, e min mbaaw- nay on nde hara ko on a√Ī…ďe nde?""